News-Classifier



To run the code use ./news_classifier.py 1 test1.txt . "test1.txt" can be replaced with any text file.

The code used serveal different categories of articles for training and classifies a new article into these categories. 

File Description:
news_classifier.py- Actual Code.
data.csv- Has training data for classifier.
Training data is inside folders.
test.txt, test2.txt, test3.txt, test4.txt, etc- Test data files

